## Topic Generation (é€‰é¢˜)

### ICP for Content
- US-based early-stage founders (especially Chinese-American)
- Building AI/SaaS/consumer products
- Open to VC investment
- Pain points: fundraising, pitching, getting investor attention

### Topic Formula
[Specific Number] + [Relatable Founder Pain] + [Unexpected Insight]

