### Weekly Content Slate
Generate 10 topics, score each by:
- ICP match (1-5)
- Novelty (1-5)
- CTA suitability (1-5)
- Production effort (1-5)

Select top 5 for the week.

## Script Generation (è„šæœ¬)

### Short Video Script (15-30s)
```
[0-3s] HOOK: Bold statement or question
[3-15s] PROBLEM: Amplify the pain point
[15-25s] INSIGHT: The key takeaway
[25-30s] CTA: "DMæˆ‘'pitch'è·å–å®Œæ•´æ¨¡ç‰ˆ"
```

### Long Video Script (45-60s)
```
[0-5s] HOOK: Pattern interrupt
[5-20s] PAIN: Show you understand their struggle
[20-45s] FRAMEWORK: 3-point insight with examples
[45-55s] PROOF: Social proof ("47 founders used this")
[55-60s] CTA: "è¯„è®º'æ¨¡ç‰ˆ'æˆ‘å‘ç»™ä½ " or "DMæˆ‘äº†è§£æ›´å¤š"
```

## Ready-to-Post Pack

Save to `workspace/xhs/content-packs/YYYY-MM-DD-{topic-slug}.md`:

```markdown
