## Posting Checklist
- [ ] Video recorded and edited
- [ ] Cover image with text overlay ready
- [ ] Caption copied
- [ ] Hashtags copied
- [ ] Post published
- [ ] First comment posted within 30 seconds
- [ ] Set timer to reply to comments for 2 hours
```

## Quality Checks (Run Before Finalizing)
- [ ] No vague claims ("best", "amazing") without specifics
- [ ] Clear CTA present
- [ ] Feels native (short lines, punchy, not corporate)
- [ ] Under 500 characters for caption
- [ ] 8-12 hashtags (not more)
- [ ] No external links in caption (links go in first comment or bio)
- [ ] Content is 60%+ original

## Posting Schedule
- 3x per week: Monday, Wednesday, Friday
- Morning US time (8-10am) = Evening China time
- Space posts at least 24 hours apart

## Content Pillars (Rotate)
1. **Fundraising Tactics** (40%) â€” pitch tips, VC insights
2. **Founder Stories** (25%) â€” rejection, imposter syndrome
3. **Market Insights** (20%) â€” what VCs fund in 2026
4. **PitchTok Product** (15%) â€” success stories, platform features
